{{vgname2|英雄联盟巴西联赛|pt=Campeonato Brasileiro de League of Legends，简称'''CBLoL'''}}是[[巴西|巴西]]地区的《[[英雄联盟|英雄联盟]]》顶级职业赛事。联赛自2021年起包含10支战队，分为春季赛和夏季赛，春季赛冠军将晋级[[英雄联盟季中邀请赛|英雄联盟季中邀请赛]]，而夏季赛冠军将晋级[[英雄联盟全球总决赛|英雄联盟全球总决赛]]<ref>{{cite news|last=Rodrigues|first=Bruno|date=2017-02-07|title=Riot anuncia Mundial 2017 na China e vaga direta para o Brasil - Mais e-Sports|newspaper=Mais e-Sports|url=https://www.maisesports.com.br/riot-anuncia-msi-2017-no-brasil-e-mundial-2017-na-china/}}</ref>。

联赛自2015年起在[[圣保罗|圣保罗]]的拳头工作室举行，并通过流媒体进行直播，除总决赛外不设观众，总决赛在[[安联公园_(巴西)|安联公园]]举行<ref>{{cite news|title=League of Legends: Riot inaugura estúdio para transmitir o Brasileiro de LoL|newspaper=TechTudo|url=http://www.techtudo.com.br/noticias/noticia/2015/01/league-legends-riot-inaugura-estudio-para-transmitir-o-brasileiro-de-lol.html}}</ref>。除在[[YouTube|YouTube]]官方频道和[[Twitch|Twitch]]上进行全方位播出外，自2017年以来，英雄联盟巴西联赛也一直在{{tsl|en|SporTV}}上进行游戏直播，其播出范围与拳头相同<ref>{{cite news|last=Oliveira|first=Gabriel|title=CBLoL 2017 começará no dia 21 com transmissão do SporTV|newspaper=CNB e-Sports Club {{!}} Gaming is our sport|url=http://mycnb.uol.com.br/noticias/5128-cblol-2017-comecara-no-dia-21-com-transmissao-do-sportv|access-date=2019-12-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170703123707/http://mycnb.uol.com.br/noticias/5128-cblol-2017-comecara-no-dia-21-com-transmissao-do-sportv|archive-date=2017-07-03|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

==概述==
英雄联盟巴西联赛从2012年开始举办，当时巴西服务器上线不久，职业化还处于起步阶段，而比赛在服务器上线三天后即举行。2014年，举办了第一届联赛：巴西联赛－冠军系列赛，同年开创了单年度两届赛事的先例，举行了巴西区冒泡赛。从那时起，巴西开始采用春夏季赛的赛制，在第一阶段各队实行“混战”（all against all），随后为淘汰赛及总决赛<ref>{{cite web|url=http://br.lolesports.com/noticias/1e7e76ac-01a6-4cf9-87b5-10b51842cdbe|title=LoLeSports BR|access-date=2017-07-10|work=br.lolesports.com}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Melo|first=Gabriel|title=Relembre as finais dos campeonatos nacionais de LoL|newspaper=CNB e-Sports Club {{!}} Gaming is our sport|url=http://mycnb.uol.com.br/noticias/4294-relembre-as-finais-dos-campeonatos-nacionais-de-league-of-legends|access-date=2019-12-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170731052221/http://mycnb.uol.com.br/noticias/4294-relembre-as-finais-dos-campeonatos-nacionais-de-league-of-legends|archive-date=2017-07-31|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。2015年，参赛队伍趋于稳定，但联赛采取了升降级制，成绩最差的队伍须降级至挑战巡回赛<ref>{{cite news|last=Set|first=Ricardo|title=CBLoL 2015 é anunciado com formato semelhante à LCS|newspaper=CNB e-Sports Club {{!}} Gaming is our sport|url=http://mycnb.uol.com.br/noticias/2123-cblol-2015-e-anunciado-com-formato-semelhante-a-lcs|access-date=2019-12-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170703145106/http://mycnb.uol.com.br/noticias/2123-cblol-2015-e-anunciado-com-formato-semelhante-a-lcs|archive-date=2017-07-03|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://br.leagueoflegends.com/pt/news/esports/esports-event/cblol-e-desafiante-na-temporada-2015|title=CBLoL e Desafiante na Temporada 2015 {{!}} League of Legends|access-date=2017-07-10|work=br.leagueoflegends.com}}</ref>。

2020年1月21日，拳头巴西确认英雄联盟巴西联赛已转为独立经营<ref>{{Cite web|title=Riot Brasil confirms CBLoL will move to franchising|url=https://www.espn.com/esports/story/_/id/28531795/riot-brasil-confirms-cblol-move-franchising|date=2020-01-22|website=ESPN}}</ref>。

